  "text": [
    "Morning\u2019s mirage, disdainful",
    "calm",
    "as a mirror,",
    "held the shorn bush that yesterday",
    "flourished,",
    "now lopped canes",
    "a scant spitfall",
    "of remnance,",
    "confetti trampled in the clefts",
    "of vanishing deer.",
    "To touch its truth I punched my fist",
    "into the chopped molest,",
    "the boscage\u2014withdrew my red sleeve.",
    "Abstract that."
  ],
  "title": "Departures: Chapter One",
